{
  "texts": [
    "This duality is categorized into 'natural language understanding' and 'natural language generation, ' forming the two pillars of NLP.",
    "However, both domains present formidable challenges.",
    "Even in the current theoretical and technological environment, creating a high-quality NLP system remains a challenging long-term goal.",
    "However, practical systems with substantial NLP capabilities have emerged for specific applications, some even achieving commercial or industrial success.",
    "Examples include multilingual database interfaces, expert systems, machine translation platforms, full-text information retrieval systems, and automatic abstracting tools."
  ]
}